    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something that looks great and runs even better without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
